_sText:
This map was created originally by Cleav420

This is #8 map i have made.

THIS MAP IS A run like HELL map!!!!!
You gotta catch a Elevator floor before everyone beats you.
There are also ladders to get up if you get there on time ROFL. 

This map is 100% better then v1
Removed spotlights/water on ground/ that made bad fps.

I add alot more hidden areas. Also moved some spawn points.
This map needed way more work on it. 
So i did a few hours of work to it.
It plays great on fps and no lagg.

So enjoy the map and please leave comment about map.

I will be working on zm_killbox_final soon because its such a small map.

Also if any one likes the few maps i made you can x-fire me @ cleav420
Or visit my ventrilo for info on how to better my maps,
Or even work with me together on one of my maps.
Thx .:{Cleav420}:.
